<section class="bg-white px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
        Roofing Questions, Answered
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
        Have questions about your roof? We have answers.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Items -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
      <details class="group border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:border-green-300 transition">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>Do you do roof replacements and repairs?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-slate-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Yes to both. We handle full roof replacements, targeted repairs for leaks, damaged shingles, and storm damage. Call for a FREE inspection and we'll tell you exactly what your roof needs—not what we want to sell you.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
      <details class="group border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:border-green-300 transition">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>What if I have a roof leak?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-slate-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Call us for a FREE inspection. We'll locate the source of the leak and give you honest advice on whether it's a quick repair or if replacement makes sense. Many leaks can be fixed fast.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
      <details class="group border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:border-green-300 transition">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>Will my insurance cover my roof damage?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-slate-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          We've worked with insurance companies extensively. Schedule a FREE inspection and we'll help you understand if your roof is covered before we start any work. We handle the insurance process with you every step of the way.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
      <details class="group border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:border-green-300 transition">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>I have storm damage—what should I do?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-slate-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Call us for a FREE inspection right away. We'll assess the damage, document everything for your insurance claim, and guide you through the whole process. Storm damage is often covered—let us help you find out.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
      <details class="group border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:border-green-300 transition">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>How do I know if my roof needs repair or replacement?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-slate-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Schedule a FREE inspection. We'll assess your roof's condition and tell you whether a targeted repair or full replacement makes sense for your situation. No obligation, no pressure—just honest advice.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
      <details class="group border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:border-green-300 transition">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>What about shingle damage or missing shingles?</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-slate-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          We repair individual shingle issues or do full replacement depending on severity and age. Get a FREE inspection to find out the best approach for your roof.
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>

    <!-- Still Have Questions CTA -->
    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Still have questions about your roof?</p>
      <a 
        href="tel:+18013168799"
        class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-green-600 text-white px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-green-700 transition duration-200"
      >
        Call Us: (801) 316-8799
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>